{"tid":1360392,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「遍地開花」濕鳩地政總署有員工反鄉黑，支持五大訴求","createTime":"2019-07-24T10:41:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T11:55:42.000Z","uid":32722,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"be0f853af29e19003faf4c87d08e555adbd1ff59","tid":1360392,"uid":32722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T10:41:25.000Z","msg":"這個地方就好似一個傳統家庭<br />\n每一位高層都係深藍，每一個office group都係維穩訊息<br />\n冇錯，呢幾年係有好多後生仔加入<br />\n但礙於上面個班老狐狸，大家都唔敢表態<br />\n<br />\n但係大家仲記唔記得爾冬陞係第35屆金像獎講過「最需要恐懼既係恐懼本身」<br />\n係，或者我只係好似謝師宴毒撚咁表態<br />\n但如果連遮樣匿名既表態都恐懼，咁仲學人爭取訴求？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KTQya9T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKTQya9T.png&h=a0fbb3d3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"39cdafd6cf9a5007a00696380071f6b8d3c47b7a","tid":1360392,"uid":38482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T10:42:17.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(呼籲!!)(汲取G20經驗)關於登報一事提升輿論問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1360136\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1360136</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"48589c123172444f746a4a9a04ba2403b85778c8","tid":1360392,"uid":32722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T11:00:57.000Z","msg":"順帶一提，做好市民，舉報丁屋僭建及非法霸佔官地！"},{"pid":"b18e262bf4678ed5adb641c7c995cd42355d51f2","tid":1360392,"uid":185960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:15:08.000Z","msg":"[文宣］黑白大字報 政權罪行 遍地開花<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1360258\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1360258</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">幫手搞臭政府！</span>"},{"pid":"7b49e6be087b9040960f5213cc8d1cab7846e986","tid":1360392,"uid":98795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:22:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0cfa04ba75f9b5a9e7ef6b49391bd9907f32c21","tid":1360392,"uid":267189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T19:46:09.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲<br />\n小弟見到好多遍地開花嘅post，好感動<br />\n不同行業嘅巴絲都出嚟發聲<br />\n<br />\n但係因為連登啲post好散同埋facebook接觸到嘅年齡層面相對連登會更加廣<br />\n所以開一個facebook page去整合一啲政府部門同公營機構嘅遍地開花post裡面嘅相<br />\n<br />\n點解淨係整政府部門同公營機構呢？<br />\n因為佢哋發聲嘅震撼力比較大同埋小弟能力有限，未能夠整合晒各行各業嘅post<br />\n<br />\n如果有巴絲其實只係想post喺連登，而唔想擺喺facebook，歡迎pm我，我會即刻delete返<br />\n<br />\n而如果有喺政府部門或者公營機構工作嘅巴絲想post去facebook，歡迎喺facebook pm呢個page: <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/civilservantsflowers\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcivilservantsflowers&d=ye2s6s2DGg0XurdvegCh9fRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=ce5d2e00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/civilservantsflowers</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山，各有各做"},{"pid":"5b7b0e229da9ad1bcca15f9d4d786d951d535e75","tid":1360392,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T11:55:42.000Z","msg":"地政總署會唔會可以係元朗霸官地問題加壓"}]}